238
00:17:18,599 --> 00:17:22,000
Nikad nisam uspio napisati
pravu ljubavnu pjesmu.

239
00:17:22,079 --> 00:17:24,319
Na Staru godinu
rekao si da želiš dijete.

240
00:17:25,279 --> 00:17:26,680
