242
00:17:30,359 --> 00:17:31,960
u Rim, je li tako?

243
00:17:35,319 --> 00:17:37,079
Bok, Rocco! Sjajni ste!

244
00:17:37,160 --> 00:17:38,680
Bok! -Bok, cure!

245
00:17:42,759 --> 00:17:47,400
NE ŽELIM VIŠE BITI TUŽNA

246
00:17:48,319 --> 00:17:49,920
Ne znam, Tommy.
