Sve što imam...

1354
01:41:09,119 --> 01:41:13,520
Sve što imam je tvoje.

1355
01:41:16,119 --> 01:41:18,119
Sve što imam...

1356
01:41:19,600 --> 01:41:21,800
Sve što imam...

1357
01:41:23,119 --> 01:41:27,079
Sve što imam je tvoje.

1358
01:41:30,239 --> 01:41:35,239
Nadvladat ću

1359
01:41:38,680 --> 01:41:44,640
strah od napuštanja.

1360
01:41:45,920 --> 01:41:50,680
Odabrat ću

1361
01:41:54,319 --> 01:42:00,119
novu kuću prema mirisu.

1362
01:42:02,520 --> 01:42:06,399
Prva je noć bez tebe.

1363
01:42:10,439 --> 01:42:14,399
Kamo je nestao sav moj svijet?

1364
01:42:16,239 --> 01:42:20,199
Budale smo jer prekidamo

1365
01:42:20,279 --> 01:42:23,720
uz toliko riječi.

1366
01:42:24,119 --> 01:42:27,720
Upuštamo se u tolike rasprave,

1367
01:42:27,800 --> 01:42:31,600
ali poludim ako osjetim tvoj miris.

1368
01:42:36,479 --> 01:42:41,720
Tražit ćeš

1369
01:42:45,159 --> 01:42:50,760
toplinu nove ljubavi.

1370
01:42:52,159 --> 01:42:57,399
Ja ću pokušati

1371
01:42:59,720 --> 01:43:03,600
izliječiti bol, kao Kintsugi.

1372
01:43:03,680 --> 01:43:06,439
Zlatno lišće na tvojim plavim očima.

1373
01:43:08,920 --> 01:43:13,000
Ali prva ti je noć bez mene.

1374
01:43:16,800 --> 01:43:20,439
Kamo je nestao sav tvoj svijet?

1375
01:43:22,600 --> 01:43:26,479
Budale smo jer prekidamo

1376
01:43:26,560 --> 01:43:30,039
uz toliko riječi.

1377
01:43:30,439 --> 01:43:34,119
Upuštamo se u tolike rasprave,

1378
01:43:34,199 --> 01:43:37,880
ali poludim ako osjetim tvoj miris.

1379
01:43:38,279 --> 01:43:41,760
Budale smo jer se volimo.

1380
01:43:42,239 --> 01:43:45,439
Nema potrebe za toliko riječi.

1381
01:43:46,039 --> 01:43:49,520
Idemo dalje, svatko svojim putem,

1382
01:43:49,880 --> 01:43:53,359
ali vratimo se tražeći ljubav

1383
01:43:54,359 --> 01:43:56,840
koja nikada ne spava,

1384
01:43:58,359 --> 01:44:00,800
koja ti kuha ono što voliš,

1385
01:44:02,239 --> 01:44:06,159
koja te svlači u 4 ujutro

1386
01:44:06,840 --> 01:44:09,079
i više ne pušta.

1387
01:44:11,000 --> 01:44:13,199
Želim drugo mjesto,

1388
01:44:13,279 --> 01:44:15,319
drugi val,

1389
01:44:15,399 --> 01:44:17,239
drugi san,

1390
01:44:17,319 --> 01:44:19,039
drugu priliku.

1391
01:44:19,119 --> 01:44:21,680
Budale smo.

1392
01:44:21,760 --> 01:44:23,239
Druga usta.

1393
01:44:23,319 --> 01:44:24,800
Drugo mjesto.

